      "writtenOn": "2020-11-03T00:16:04Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "left some comments for things that are needed. I would really focus on those, maybe create a separate CL focused on those (this CL is trying to do a lot of things, IMO too much).\n\nin particular, I think Watcher/EventListener is a premature generalization: https://wiki.c2.com/?PrematureGeneralizationIsEvil",
      "parentUuid": "13a33120_d326c725",
      "revId": "685ae912a3f4371c3dfa2fd9ea5292076d78864d",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
